Claude CodeCursorAuto Setup Wizard <p>Add to <code>~/.claude.json</code>:</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "engram": {
      "command": "engram-mcp",
      "env": { "GEMINI_API_KEY": "your-key" }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Add to Cursor's MCP settings:</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "engram": {
      "command": "engram-mcp",
      "env": { "GEMINI_API_KEY": "your-key" }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <pre><code>engram setup
</code></pre> <p>The wizard auto-detects installed agents (Claude Code, Cursor, OpenClaw, Windsurf, etc.) and configures them interactively.</p>
